included.summary:
I am a User Researcher, holding a Master's degree in Human Computer Interaction and a PhD in media studies. I have more than 10 years of research experience in the  for profit, nonprofit, and academic sectors. 

In my work, I research, explore, and design solutions that facilitate the smooth and ethical integration of technologies in users' lives. I believe in seeking original approaches to social problems and exploring uncharted paths in design and social computing. 

Specialties: UX Research Methods; Interaction Design; Participatory Design; Contextual Inquiry; Social Media Research
